summary: I am a motivated IT executive with  proven track record supporting a company from small regional player to multi-billion dollar publicly traded organization.  This has given me insight into the varying perspectives of organizations of different sizes and their needs.  From the early days where the future of the organization could rely on the speed of a single deployment, through to the growing pains of bringing standardization and scale in an organization where annual acquisitions were measured in the dozens and annual location increases in the hundreds.
